# 11. Command Palette (Master Shortcut)

## Open Command Palette

```text
Ctrl + Shift + P
```

You can do almost anything from here:

* Git commands
* Kubernetes extensions
* Terraform commands
* Format document
* Restart language server

Think of this as VS Code's "Google Search".

