# 13. Git Productivity Shortcuts

## Open Source Control

```text
Ctrl + Shift + G
```

## View Changes

Click file in Source Control.

### Daily Git Flow

```bash
git pull
git checkout -b feature/new-feature
git add .
git commit -m "added deployment"
git push
```

Use VS Code Git UI whenever possible.

